[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]There is no acknowledgement 
[normal]in 
[normal]these
[normal] new policy documents of the principle of induced traffic or that 
[normal]the new 
[normal]policies, ostensibly designed to tackle growing traffic, will in fact be responsible for making the problem worse. These are not controversial sta
[normal]tements to make. T
[normal]hese principl
[normal]es have been 
