[normal]B) Recent [bold]changes in [bold]traffic trends[bold]Traffic 
[normal]in
[normal] Great Britain has 
[normal]diverged
[normal] from historical trends in 
[normal]the past two decades
[normal].
[normal] 
[normal]There 
[normal]has been
[normal] a flattening of growth 
[normal]since 
