[normal]DfT traffic statistics for 2012 show th
[normal]at the
[normal] total
[normal] amount of traffic is now below 
[normal]that
[normal] 
[normal]of 
[normal]2003
[normal].
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]The most recent National Travel Survey 
[normal](NTS)
[normal] illustrates how driving patterns are changing on a per-person basis
[normal]. 
[normal]Key results
[normal] include:
[normal],
[normal]These trends all call into question the wisdom 
[normal]of building new roads now. C
[normal]ongestion and traffic are below wha
[normal]t they have been at their peak, with several years of growth needed just to bring them up to levels that have previously been experienced. Far better to take advantage of the 'breathing space' provided by the recent trends 
[normal]to support sustainable transport 
[normal]alternatives.
